			"content": "<script lang=\"ts\">\n\tinterface IconProps {\n\t\tcolor?: string;\n\t\tsize?: number;\n\t\tstrokeWidth?: number;\n\t\tanimate?: boolean;\n\t\tclass?: string;\n\t}\n\n\tlet {\n\t\tcolor = 'currentColor',\n\t\tsize = 24,\n\t\tstrokeWidth = 2,\n\t\tanimate = false,\n\t\tclass: className = ''\n\t}: IconProps = $props();\n\n\tconst circles = [\n\t\t{ cx: 19, cy: 5, delay: 0 }, // Top right\n\t\t{ cx: 12, cy: 5, delay: 0.05 }, // Top middle\n\t\t{ cx: 19, cy: 12, delay: 0.1 }, // Middle right\n\t\t{ cx: 5, cy: 5, delay: 0.15 }, // Top left\n\t\t{ cx: 12, cy: 12, delay: 0.2 }, // Center\n\t\t{ cx: 19, cy: 19, delay: 0.25 }, // Bottom right\n\t\t{ cx: 5, cy: 12, delay: 0.3 }, // Middle left\n\t\t{ cx: 12, cy: 19, delay: 0.35 }, // Bottom middle\n\t\t{ cx: 5, cy: 19, delay: 0.4 } // Bottom left\n\t];\n\n\tfunction handleMouseEnter() {\n\t\tif (animate) return;\n\t\tanimate = true;\n\n\t\tsetTimeout(() => {\n\t\t\tanimate = false;\n\t\t}, 1600);\n\t}\n</script>\n\n<div class={className} aria-label=\"grip\" role=\"img\" onmouseenter={handleMouseEnter}>\n\t<svg\n\t\txmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\n\t\twidth={size}\n\t\theight={size}\n\t\tviewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n\t\tfill=\"none\"\n\t\tstroke={color}\n\t\tstroke-width={strokeWidth}\n\t\tstroke-linecap=\"round\"\n\t\tstroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n\t\tclass=\"grip-icon\"\n\t>\n\t\t{#each circles as { cx, cy, delay }}\n\t\t\t<circle\n\t\t\t\t{cx}\n\t\t\t\t{cy}\n\t\t\t\tr=\"1\"\n\t\t\t\tclass=\"grip-circle\"\n\t\t\t\tclass:animate\n\t\t\t\tstyle=\"animation-delay: {delay}s;\"\n\t\t\t/>\n\t\t{/each}\n\t</svg>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n\tdiv {\n\t\tdisplay: inline-block;\n\t}\n\t.grip-icon {\n\t\toverflow: visible;\n\t}\n\n\t.grip-circle {\n\t\topacity: 1;\n\t}\n\n\t@keyframes fadeInOut {\n\t\t0%,\n\t\t100% {\n\t\t\topacity: 1;\n\t\t}\n\t\t50% {\n\t\t\topacity: 0.3;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t.grip-circle.animate {\n\t\tanimation: fadeInOut 0.8s ease-in forwards;\n\t}\n</style>\n"
